---
import CodeBlock from '../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
import LocalizedPage from '../../components/LocalizedPage.astro';

import { docSeo } from '../../data/seo';
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';

const seo = docSeo('getting-started');
---

<DocsLayout
  title={seo.title}
  description={seo.description}
  canonicalPath={seo.path}
  active="getting-started"
  schemaType={seo.schemaType}
  breadcrumbs={seo.breadcrumbs}
  tocAuto
>
  <LocalizedPage>
    <Fragment slot="en">
      <h1>Getting Started</h1>
      <p>
        AnyUI ships a single package with framework-scoped entrypoints for Vue, React and Svelte,
        plus a shared stylesheet that carries the design tokens, themes and the optional liquid
        glass style.
      </p>

      <h2>Install</h2>
      <CodeBlock lang="bash" code={`pnpm add @any-design/anyui`} />

      <p>
        Or install headlessly through the shadcn-compatible registry. For the full adapter workflow,
        see the <a href="/docs/shadcn-registry">shadcn Registry guide</a>.
      </p>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="bash"
        code={`pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/vue --yes --silent
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/react --yes --silent
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/svelte --yes --silent`}
      />

      <h2>Vue</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="ts"
        code={`import { createApp } from 'vue';
import AnyUI from '@any-design/anyui/vue';
import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';

const app = createApp(App);
app.use(AnyUI);
app.mount('#app');`}
      />
      <p>
        For on-demand imports, use the bundled resolver with <code>unplugin-vue-components</code> —
        see the README for the full Vite setup.
      </p>

      <h2>React</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="tsx"
        code={`import { Button, Card, Input, message } from '@any-design/anyui/react';
import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Card title="Hello">
      <Input placeholder="Type something cute..." round />
      <Button type="primary" round onClick={() => message.success('Hi! 🎉')}>
        Greet
      </Button>
    </Card>
  );
}`}
      />

      <h2>Svelte</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="svelte"
        code={`<script lang="ts">
  import { Button, Card, Input, message } from '@any-design/anyui/svelte';
  import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';
</script>

<Card title="Hello">
  <Input placeholder="Type something cute..." round />
  <Button type="primary" round onClick={() => message.success('Hi! 🎉')}>Greet</Button>
</Card>`}
      />

      <h2>Enable liquid glass</h2>
      <p>Add one attribute on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> (or scope it with <code>.a-glass</code>):</p>
      <CodeBlock lang="html" code={`<html data-anyui-style="glass">`} />
      <p>
        Every surface component turns translucent with a backdrop blur and specular highlight, in
        both light and dark themes. Try the Glass toggle in this site's header.
      </p>

      <h2>Dark theme</h2>
      <p>
        The dark palette is derived automatically from your theme colors. Activate it manually with
        <code>&lt;html theme="dark"&gt;</code>, or let the user's system preference apply it via the
        built-in <code>prefers-color-scheme</code> media query.
      </p>

      <h2>Next steps</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/components">Components</a> — browse every component, with props, events and slots.</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/shadcn-registry">shadcn Registry</a> — install with an app-local adapter.</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/tokens">Design Tokens</a> — radii, motion, elevation and surfaces.</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/theming">Theme Customization</a> — re-color the system via SCSS.</li>
        <li>
          <a href="/testground/" data-astro-reload>Testground</a> — every component, all three
          frameworks, side by side.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="zh">
      <h1>快速开始</h1>
      <p>
        AnyUI 通过一个包提供 Vue、React 和 Svelte 的框架入口，并附带一份共享样式表。设计令牌、主题、暗色模式和可选的 liquid glass 风格都由这份样式承载。
      </p>

      <h2>安装</h2>
      <CodeBlock lang="bash" code={`pnpm add @any-design/anyui`} />

      <p>
        也可以通过兼容 shadcn 的 registry 以无头方式安装。完整 adapter 流程见
        <a href="/docs/shadcn-registry">shadcn Registry 安装指南</a>。
      </p>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="bash"
        code={`pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/vue --yes --silent
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/react --yes --silent
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add any-design/anyui/svelte --yes --silent`}
      />

      <h2>Vue</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="ts"
        code={`import { createApp } from 'vue';
import AnyUI from '@any-design/anyui/vue';
import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';

const app = createApp(App);
app.use(AnyUI);
app.mount('#app');`}
      />
      <p>
        如果需要按需导入，可以配合内置 resolver 和 <code>unplugin-vue-components</code> 使用；完整 Vite 配置见 README。
      </p>

      <h2>React</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="tsx"
        code={`import { Button, Card, Input, message } from '@any-design/anyui/react';
import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Card title="Hello">
      <Input placeholder="Type something cute..." round />
      <Button type="primary" round onClick={() => message.success('Hi! 🎉')}>
        Greet
      </Button>
    </Card>
  );
}`}
      />

      <h2>Svelte</h2>
      <CodeBlock
        lang="svelte"
        code={`<script lang="ts">
  import { Button, Card, Input, message } from '@any-design/anyui/svelte';
  import '@any-design/anyui/styles/index.css';
</script>

<Card title="Hello">
  <Input placeholder="Type something cute..." round />
  <Button type="primary" round onClick={() => message.success('Hi! 🎉')}>Greet</Button>
</Card>`}
      />

      <h2>启用 liquid glass</h2>
      <p>在 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 上添加一个属性即可全局启用，也可以用 <code>.a-glass</code> 局部启用：</p>
      <CodeBlock lang="html" code={`<html data-anyui-style="glass">`} />
      <p>
        启用后，表面组件会变成带 backdrop blur 与内侧高光的半透明形态，并同时适配浅色和暗色主题。你可以直接试用站点导航里的 Glass 开关。
      </p>

      <h2>暗色主题</h2>
      <p>
        暗色调色盘会从主题色自动推导。你可以通过 <code>&lt;html theme="dark"&gt;</code> 手动启用，也可以让内置的
        <code>prefers-color-scheme</code> 媒体查询跟随系统偏好。
      </p>

      <h2>下一步</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/components">组件</a>：浏览所有组件以及 props、events、slots。</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/shadcn-registry">shadcn Registry</a>：通过应用内 adapter 安装。</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/tokens">设计令牌</a>：了解圆角、动效、阴影和表面抽象层。</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/theming">主题定制</a>：通过 SCSS 重新定义系统颜色。</li>
        <li>
          <a href="/testground/" data-astro-reload>Testground</a>：并排查看三个框架里的所有组件。
        </li>
      </ul>
    </Fragment>
  </LocalizedPage>
</DocsLayout>
